ber":"13792","dbdateline":"1454328514","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"31468332","tid":"1085129","first":"0","author":"starring","authorid":"250983","dateline":"2016-2-1 20:47","message":"<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/6d670f29gw1f0k4hqhgsaj20g40n8jt9.jpg\" width=\"580\" height=\"836\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《终将成为你》的作者，在访谈中提到京吹了<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face/17.gif\" /><br />\r<br />\r<br />\r<div class=\"reply_wrap\">——原来如此。仲谷老师最近有觉得不错的百合作品吗？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲谷：我很喜欢动画『吹响吧！悠风号』。都有种自己想在百合方面描绘的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n内容被抢先展现出来了的感觉。「为啥我要一边看这个一边画百合漫画啦」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心情都变得有些奇怪了（笑）。学生时代我也是吹奏乐部的部员。中学是长<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n号，高中是大号。作为元吹奏乐部的一员，故事中很多地方都让我产生了共<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鸣，再加上百合味儿十足真是让我喜欢得不得了！乐器的作画也很厉害，正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因为演奏过乐器才能发现的细节也有很多，这部动画实在是太合我的胃口了，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真的十分感谢！。</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://card.weibo.com/article/h5/s#cid=1001603901531744303155&amp;from=1055093010&amp;wm=3333_2001&amp;ip=117.131.3.70\">http://card.weibo.com/article/h5 ... amp;ip=117.131.3.70</a>","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"14287","username":"starring","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"13793","dbdateline":"1454330869","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"31469095","tid":"1085129","first":"0","author":"shinnfin","authorid":"230035","dateline":"2016-2-1 22:43","message":"他果然看过京吹！","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"14288","username":"shinnfin","adminid":"-1","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"13794","dbdateline":"1454337780","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"31469333","tid":"1085129","first":"0","author":"心之渊","authorid":"219246","dateline":"2016-2-1 23:13","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=31467369&amp;ptid=1085129\"><font color=\"#999999\">巴啦啦小兔兔儿 发表于 2016-